<dt class="yellow">Journal</dt><dd><em>Science Bulletin</em></dd>


<dt class="green">Funder</dt><dd>National Science Foundation of China/Research Grants Council Joint Research Scheme, Grant from City University of Hong Kong, Science & Technology Department of Sichuan Province</dd>

</dl>

</a>
</article>
